Ask HN: Bitwarden password Helper delay on Android Google Chrome
text:
When I login to a website on chrome and try to get Bitwarden Password helper to show up on the bar above the keyboard to assist it either appears with a delay or not at all and I have to manually open Bitwarden and copy creds or even show up. This delay is absent in the android Firefox browser. Here is a screenshot of without https://i.imgur.com/rWKlomu.png and with: https://i.imgur.com/cTl296L.png the Bitwarden helper.

Have others experienced the same thing?

How do my I test that this is a bug or intentional?
